<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다 - My Universe</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            background: #f0f2f5;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            background: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        a:hover {
            background: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>404</h1>
        <p>
            <%= message || '요청하신 페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다.' %>
        </p>
        <% if (locals.blog) { %>
            <a href="/">블로그 홈으로</a>
            <% } else { %>
                <a href="https://pong2.app">메인으로 이동</a>
                <% } %>
    </div>
</body>

</html>